General.Name: Sparebank 68 Grader Nord
General.Description: Sparebank 68° Nord operates as a savings bank that provides a range of banking services to private customers and companies in Norway. The company offers savings accounts; mortgage, car and other vehicle, and small loans, as well as business and construction loans; bank guarantees, overdrafts, and leasing products; online and mobile banking, card, and payment services; insurance and pension services; and mortgage and home insurance. The company is based in Harstad, Norway.
